      "comment": "HARA'S HAZEL (1) is first up since finishing sixth (30.54) in a Grade 6 at Q Parklands over 520m 12 weeks ago. Overall form off this box is sound. Rates strongly and will go close from the inside draw. CANYA FAKE IT (4) is yet to miss the placings in four starts including two wins and finished in the minor money again last time when second (25.88) over 457m at this track. Will go close here with a clear run. PAID IN GLORY (3) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Maiden at Q Parklands. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Can turn it around this time. SON OF RUPEE (2) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
